{"tid":2220244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美法院駁回TikTok用戶阻程式下架申請","createTime":"2020-09-27T13:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T14:27:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c0394df8cfb78ab55db81b48157f786975b5a278","tid":2220244,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"美法院駁回TikTok用戶阻程式下架申請<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407087&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=7d82e346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407087&h=3bc34c03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407087</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國要求手機應用程式商店將TikTok下架的禁令，將在當地周日晚生效，法院將在禁令生效前，處理挑戰禁令的申請，另外有美國TikTok用戶阻止禁令的申請被駁回。<br />\n<br />\n三名入稟的TikTok內容創作者指，TikTok下架會令他們損失數以萬計的潛在觀眾及創作者。賓夕法尼亞州地方法院法官指，程式下架無疑會帶來不便，但他們仍然可以在程式內，向現有數以百萬計用戶創作、發布及分享內容，因此駁回申請。<br />\n<br />\n至於字節跳動入稟的臨時禁制令申請，華盛頓地方法院會在美國時間周日早上開庭，趕在禁令晚上生效前處理。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部早前延長禁令生效時間一星期至周日，讓字節跳動、甲骨文及沃爾瑪完成交易，由新成立的公司接管TikTok美國業務。"},{"pid":"ed9bb681428ff3cfa83f5a54e5340d8e0c015810","tid":2220244,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549194390c062c18ce3c65e52ca7646b97c745da","tid":2220244,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ada9d47ec